<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_6f744ae9-c59b-4556-8c63-a025f7a90ebc" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>J1V1</sptc><title id="_531f9b6a-5c5a-46d5-afc2-749ff02cec5b">NABERS Energy</title><archive-num>2019: JV1</archive-num><subclause id="_05c76cff-b4e7-45d6-8ee7-4502420fbb93" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ecf5c36c-27db-44ff-a12c-8ff3c4c0b7a4">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For a Class 5 building, compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/7883_0.3.0.xml#_785e395a-703b-4da2-b1f9-27284ff5af75" id="_9be719cf-600f-498e-ad5d-788445f2c352" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NSW J1P1</xref> is verified when—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ee50b72e-467c-4130-88fd-1773d4a096bb">a minimum 6-star <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_ab159aa2-39e5-4dde-985b-212ba1e14b20" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for offices base building Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_294bea3c-7915-47af-9571-aa7ed5c3f1d9">the energy model required for (a) demonstrates that the base building’s <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_3ef32de9-2a9f-4d83-bbf5-4af936f51354" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy</xref> greenhouse gas emissions are equivalent to at least the 6.6 star level when excluding—<ol><li>tenant supplementary heating and cooling systems; and</li><li>external lighting; and</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1213_1.0.0.xml#_1b0c2237-d3d4-4981-97b8-209936e55520" id="_1866a3e7-0ec5-4455-9096-2fd1e7a98dd1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">carpark</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_316728df-bb28-431f-a80d-08940a8876fc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_186b7c38-e2fc-4810-a626-9fc820182c21">the energy model required for (a) demonstrates either—<ol><li>a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1489_0.6.0.xml#_49deeede-a813-43a8-a61d-cfbe54ddb6d8" id="_6d3b8b5b-22c9-496a-830e-58f1c4348703" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">thermal comfort level</xref> of between a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1404_0.4.0.xml#_50155542-eddc-47be-acea-a15f2c017dea" id="_a2535e4e-6915-4d0b-bfc4-6c77c1903e24" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Predicted Mean Vote</xref> of -1 to +1 is achieved across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_aae21b92-714d-40a6-a687-47ed164372ef" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones for not less than 98% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_da76aabd-ce3d-4c47-9cbe-86d0c1c03b6e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> of the building; or</li><li>a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_af881592-6111-4a0c-8312-a8826555c93e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_53b62376-fd15-4afa-8eff-faadba450afc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_f2801ad6-def3-4ed1-9d97-ea58418df1b7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_1b3f7f78-b778-4bd9-8084-04c05b03d126" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_b3d5a2ee-b2ec-4219-b416-8e50fb806eb1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_bf75a226-c026-4de2-ba77-4e33475f8567">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_7846e9ce-2ee8-4ec8-9d44-f9adc5742f2e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_2771d6ba-bfe8-43d0-991c-3915580b85e4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_79a75dfa-8861-4a2f-9f64-508608a40ce0">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>For a Class 3 building, compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/7883_0.3.0.xml#_785e395a-703b-4da2-b1f9-27284ff5af75" id="_cb0a87f4-188f-4385-b18a-a6f7e83d3d35" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NSW J1P1</xref> is verified when— </p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b0e165bf-6b38-4798-ac7b-e5124b12b44a">a minimum 4-star <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_22c52e38-ed33-4435-bbce-0a42fcdda912" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Hotels Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_c3553c85-b27f-4270-91b9-5f1ea4725770">the operating hours of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_d4ca2206-fa0b-48e7-a384-90f36ecad467" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref> are not less than 12 hours per day in bedrooms, dining rooms and conference facilities, 24 hours per day in corridors and foyers and 18 hours per day in back-of-house areas; and</li><li id="_3e51eb42-5fc2-4769-9890-e8b339026869">the energy model <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_2fa1eb62-eccf-46ac-8d2d-b11fad434596" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for (a) demonstrates that— <ol><li>the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_db03da0d-1bd6-4da2-b95a-355671a0cc56" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy</xref> greenhouse gas emissions are equivalent to at least 5.3 stars; and</li><li>a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_461ff380-7b81-49a2-88a8-a8d6e97b78d3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_6e97db52-3ac6-47c1-80d5-2a5f0d974196" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_b4fa9869-8e37-48ac-8335-f051b8f264c1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_7fecedb2-f6ba-4647-bc7b-549579d82453" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy and food preparation areas; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_0bb346df-94f4-434e-9cd0-a2c2c8f25000" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li>the space temperature in any indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_b7896519-dee6-4868-8aa8-fa711355444b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> chamber is maintained at 2°C above the pool temperature during occupied hours of not less than 12 hours per day; and</li></ol></li><li id="_1f804114-a3d1-482a-8966-94bc959b0746">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_7300fd88-69e0-4145-b748-7578417efd1f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f42d6710-e211-41fd-a2ce-7514ffb4edd6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_25984273-4dc7-40bc-a632-69d8580a38c4">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>For a Class 6 shopping centre, compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/7883_0.3.0.xml#_785e395a-703b-4da2-b1f9-27284ff5af75" id="_c9f5ba75-b18e-441c-b737-b57a0f9d5d29" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NSW J1P1</xref> is verified when—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_890118f6-4e88-4357-9695-be8b95e83517">a minimum 6-stars <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_43cef499-7866-4e0b-a8c0-8dad1fa592fe" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Shopping Centres Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_7f710710-2143-4a4a-bfdc-f05896006796">the building has:<ol><li id="">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_d89e5a85-6b2d-4258-817a-67a93be77588" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioned</xref> common area of not less than 20% of the gross lettable area; and</li><li>a gross lettable area greater than 15 000 m<sup id="_bb181963-ddb9-4e98-b3f5-b23f1f08ac59">2</sup>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_a0c1d357-b022-493f-876d-5771b3c637ae">the energy model <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_6ea2a315-4dfd-4263-8eca-6e9e53582058" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for (a) demonstrates—<ol><li>the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_090bbbc1-7915-4f7a-b298-1e98cfaed42f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy</xref> greenhouse gas emissions of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_ab1c90a8-8a5c-43e6-9140-98851ae8027c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref> covered within the scope of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_7588da2e-7a34-4933-aa3c-c43477b791bf" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Shopping Centres ratings are equivalent to at least 6.7 stars when—<ol><li>excluding carpark services and carpark numbers from <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_103623e4-b757-4d19-bb0f-715da54c792b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> calculation; and</li><li>calculating solar photovoltaic export based on the reduced site energy use arising from (A); and</li></ol></li><li id="">a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_c1242387-fbd7-4951-98fb-89c2afd8390e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_167bb80a-8394-46e3-9dac-e1ef4fd979d5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_77153ace-91ad-474a-8a06-420aa2a0d3ae" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_623a994c-a028-4cec-a380-59a60ccc1fd8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy and food preparation areas; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_e3eec5aa-182e-4f15-b60d-a6c6ffc838cd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_58ea6ca2-9fda-4a64-9941-92adf4bba955">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_1eaa0866-3942-4842-b28b-5626a875fe09" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_367d89f4-d804-4da0-be86-4f146ef23d96" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4e1f5a79-ee4c-4223-baa3-8379f1336984">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The calculation method for (1), (2) and (3) must comply with ANSI/ASHRAE Standard 140.</p></subclause></clause>